    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2008-04-17</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2008-05-14T18:07:31Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to suspend excise taxes on gasoline and diesel fuels between May 26, 2008, and September 1, 2008. Provides for reimbursement from the Treasury to the Highway Trust Fund for any reduction in Trust Fund receipts resulting from such suspension.</p><p>Expresses the policy of Congress that: (1) consumers immediately receive the benefit of the reduction in taxes resulting from this Act; and (2) transportation motor fuels producers and other dealers take necessary actions to reduce fuel prices to reflect such reduction in taxes. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
